high_descs: Go to the right side of the coffee table.
Pick up the yellow pencil.
Turn around and look at the couch.
Place the pencil in the box.
Pick up the box.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the table.
Place the box on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a box with a pencil in it on a table.

high_descs: Move to the coffee table.
Pick up the pencil from the coffee table.
Bring the pencil to the box on the couch.
Put the pencil in the box.
Pick up the box from the couch.
Bring the box to the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a pencil in it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking forward, then turn left and walk over to the pencil on the coffee table.
Pick up the pencil off of the coffee table.
Turn left, take a step forward then turn left again to face the cardboard box on the couch.
Place the pencil inside the cardboard box.
Pick up the cardboard box with the pencil inside it up off of the couch.
Turn left, begin walking to the door, then hang a left and continue forwards towards the fireplace, stop and turn left when at the end of the coffee table.
Place the cardboard box with the pencil in it onto the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cardboard box with a pencil in it onto the coffee table.
